## Product star rating

You can display the product rating using the Rating widget, by populating it with dynamic tags from **Post  Reviews  Average rating**. As the dynamic tag returns an empty value when there are no reviews, you can apply a **Fallback mod** and type **0**

![](data:image/png;base64,)

Similarly, you can display the number of reviews using a text based widget and populating with dynamic tags from **Post  Reviews  Total count**
